Provide a CMake custom command and pseudo-target, backed by a script under cmake/scripts/, that reads $BUILDDIR/generated/class_names.json (goal 04) and generates the C++ source file(s) defining the print_members / debug-print functions for every struct and class under src/ava/, writing them under $BUILDDIR/generated/. The generator runs automatically only when class_names.json is newer than the generated sources, or the sources are missing; otherwise it is refreshed on demand as part of the manual generation chain.
